    "109952774": {
      "title": "Collect and release data on coercive police actions",
      "abstract": "During that same year, how many times did policeofficers use their batons or chemical spray during encounters with peoplein any given community? How many high-speed police pursuits ended incollisions? How many vehicle stops last year in any given community ledto vehicle searches, and what was the racial composition of those searchedas compared with those stopped? All of these questions have the sameanswer:"
    }
